io.github.jonestimd.swing.table.model

Interface MixedRowTableModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ColumnIdentifier, TableModel
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BufferedHeaderDetailTableModel, HeaderDetailTableModel

    public interface MixedRowTableModel
extends TableModel, ColumnIdentifier
    This interface defines the data model API for a MixedRowTable. The rows are arranged in groups. Each group contains one or more sub-rows in any combination of sub-row types. All sub-row types must have the same number of columns.
